{"tid":678353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple 將會在 6 月「解封」 iPhone NFC 限制！","createTime":"2018-05-26T04:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T06:51:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"262f8616979f97f418a109a16b61c3dd2ef1ffd1","tid":678353,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"從 2014 年的 iPhone 6 開始，新的 iPhone 已含有 NFC 支援，不過除了 Apple Pay 外，Apple 一直在 NFC 上的應用走得相當慢，最多也只是對自家產品裡配合使用，又或者在日本／中國試行交通卡上的整合。不過，一般的開發者並不能隨意使用 NFC。<br />\n<br />\n來自 The Information 的報導指，Apple 有意在今年 6 月的 WWDC 2018 裡宣佈 NFC 應用上的轉變，例如開放 iPhone 上的 NFC 功能讓開發者使用，當然這功能必須在 iOS 12 上才可啟動。這改變很有可能同時對 Apple Watch 進行，因為 Apple Watch 也同時具備 NFC 支援能力。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，iOS 11 裡，Apple 已經容許 iPhone 7/iPhone 8 透過 Core NFC APPI 來讀取 NFC Tag。其實，Apple 員工已經可以用 iPhone 來對 Apple Park（新總部）的門進行解鎖，而 watchOS 4 裡的 GymKit 其實也使用上 NFC 功能。估計，WWDC 2018 裡，開發者會得到更多關於 NFC 上的新應用方式。iPhone 用戶在 NFC 功能開放後，相信會有更多便利生活的應用出現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/26/apple-unlock-nfc-2018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2Fapple-unlock-nfc-2018%2F&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c46db422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/26/apple-unlock-nfc-2018/</a>"},{"pid":"677591180bd70007323a4be43ed48389aff958ad","tid":678353,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1f1191da4340a56ba8160312667da84500e44f","tid":678353,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea386d6e607d1a0095b246233b5b9c20718404f","tid":678353,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T06:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}